EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY 24 AND 26 SEP
   WITHIN 37 MILES OF 57-30.2N 009-00.8W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
   PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2281/14.
3. CANCEL THIS MSG 262000Z SEP 14.
